beer.beer_description: A West coast IPA with mathematically outrageous amounts of Centennial, Citra, and Mosaic. By utilising 3 different hop products and processes of these 3 types of heavy hitters we're able to bring the old school into the new world. We're on a journey from lofty Pines of Oregon, down through the orange groves by the Sierras, and onward to the tropical Pacific shore where ocean laps this gracious land of IPA. Its hip to be cubed.
